en Waffen ab und flieht</a></div></div><div class="top-in-tabs__item"><div class="top-in-tabs__index">2</div><div class="top-in-tabs__header"><a href="/kurzclips/104454-israel-tausende-protestieren-gegen-management/" class="link">Israel: Tausende protestieren gegen Management in der Corona-Krise und fordern Soforthilfen</a></div></div><div class="top-in-tabs__item"><div class="top-in-tabs__index">3</div><div class="top-in-tabs__header"><a href="/kurzclips/104449-stuttgart-hunderte-protestieren-gegen-corona-massnahmen/" class="link">Stuttgart: Hunderte protestieren gegen Corona-Maßnahmen – Zahlreiche Insolvenzen befürchtet</a></div></div><div class="top-in-tabs__item"><div class="top-in-tabs__index">4</div><div class="top-in-tabs__header"><a href="/kurzclips/104455-portland-black-lives-matter-proteste/" class="link">Portland: "Black Lives Matter"-Proteste schlagen erneut in Gewalt um</a></div></div><div class="top-in-tabs__item"><div class="top-in-tabs__index">5</div><div class="top-in-tabs__header"><a href="/live/104495-live-paris-anti-regierungs-proteste/" class="link">LIVE: Paris – Anti-Regierungs-Proteste am französischen Nationalfeiertag</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="column__cell"><a class="top-privacy-policy" href="/privacy-policy"><h1>Datenschutzerklärung</h1></a></div></div><div class="column__row mb-3"><div class="column__cell"><div class="banners"><!-- DE_RT_International - Box --><div id="div-gpt-ad-1486974609321-1"><script>
